
This is the Perl distribution Class-Method-Debug.

## Installation

Class-Method-Debug installation is straightforward.
If your CPAN shell is set up, you should just be able to do

    % cpan Class::Method::Debug

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

## Documentation

Class-Method-Debug documentation is available as in POD.
So you can do:

    % perldoc Class::Method::Debug

to read the documentation with your favorite pager.
